util

类 TransformMatrix

  • java.lang.Object
    • util.TransformMatrix

  • public class TransformMatrix
extends java.lang.Object
    A class to process the rotation and flip of a matrix, there are up to 8 positions.
    版本:
    0.1 11/18, 1.0 11/22 1 Add flip operation. 2 Change the name of the class from "RotateMatrix" to "TransformMatrix".
    作者:
    David
